{"tid":1258773,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【輸錢有樣睇?】澳門賭場擬引入AI技術 尋找「黑仔」賭客","createTime":"2019-06-26T09:24:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T11:03:03.000Z","uid":38172,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f54a62ea312dbcb10f899c6f9d3b986fc982834d","tid":1258773,"uid":38172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T09:24:35.000Z","msg":"據彭博報道，近期澳門賭場陸續引入人工智能技術，透過隱蔽鏡頭、人面辨識等技術、設有電子晶片的籌碼，以及特別設計的百家樂枱等，追蹤有較大機會「輸大錢」的賭客，報道指，金沙中國及美高梅中國已開始引入這類技術，其中金沙計劃在至少1000張賭枱上加入這類技術，而永利、銀娛及新濠博亞則正在研究。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，賭場透過人工智能技術找出「有可能大額下注並輸掉的賭客」時，可以向他們埋手，「特別照顧他們、甚至提供額外的優惠」，令他們繼續留在賭場遊玩並輸錢；同時可利用技術識別這類「黑仔」賭客大手下注的時機，而在大手下注的情況下，賭場的贏率一般較平常高10倍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1561535452310&amp;issue=20190626&amp;fbclid=IwAR29pVMQxys8RxSzjTrXfDiX6tUGzfgVhmoj5JVtaWC-7LBQqG_kutMZ9Vo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1561535452310%26issue%3D20190626%26fbclid%3DIwAR29pVMQxys8RxSzjTrXfDiX6tUGzfgVhmoj5JVtaWC-7LBQqG_kutMZ9Vo&d=BBPgAQHQe62%2Fb%2Fw120tVmcRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=be4d94ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1561535452310&amp;issue=20190626&amp;fbclid=IwAR29pVMQxys8RxSzjTrXfDiX6tUGzfgVhmoj5JVtaWC-7LBQqG_kutMZ9Vo</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/XmdJpCXgpz8/sddefault.jpg#404_is_fine\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FXmdJpCXgpz8%2Fsddefault.jpg%23404_is_fine&h=a24ec504&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今次真係電腦分析 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcfd0414c9ebb3ad3a37dde49a69263ac8808759","tid":1258773,"uid":38218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T11:03:03.000Z","msg":"風水命理+AI"}]}